          content, nor for any actions taken based on the information provided.
          Use of the Website is at the user’s own risk.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium mt-8">
          Intellectual Property
        </h2>

        <p>
          All content on this Website, including texts, designs, logos, and
          graphics, is the property of Madrid Landing Kit unless otherwise stated.
          Unauthorized use is prohibited.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium mt-8">
          Applicable Law
        </h2>

        <p>
          This Legal Notice is governed by Spanish law. Any disputes arising from
          the use of this Website shall be subject to the jurisdiction of the
          courts of Madrid, Spain.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium mt-8">
          Contact
        </h2>

        <p>
          Email: <a href="mailto:info@madridlandingkit.com" class="underline">
            info@madridlandingkit.com
          </a>
        </p>

      </div>
    </Wrapper>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

